          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">Chose <strong class="text-gray-900">Webnode</strong> for "EU hosting" and "GDPR compliance."</strong></p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">Spent ‚Ç¨8,000 on custom theme development to make dated templates look modern.</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Launch result: <strong class="text-red-600">1.8% conversion rate</strong>. Industry average: 3.2%.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border-[2px] border-[#0033CC] p-6 mb-6">
          <p class="text-xs font-black text-[#0033CC] uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">The Problem</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">Site looked <strong class="text-gray-900">dated</strong>. Despite custom theme investment, underlying framework limited design.</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">Surveyed 50 customers. Response: <strong class="text-gray-900">"Looks like a website from 2020."</strong></p>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Customers couldn't articulate why, but <strong class="text-[#0033CC]">trust was lower</strong>.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border-[2px] border-[#0033CC] p-6 mb-6">
          <p class="text-xs font-black text-[#0033CC] uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">The Fix</p>
