            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="bg-[#0033CC] text-white text-xs font-black px-2 py-1 rounded flex-shrink-0">DAY 1</span>
              <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Wix site live. Modern design. GDPR banner configured. Cookie consent working.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="bg-[#0033CC] text-white text-xs font-black px-2 py-1 rounded flex-shrink-0">DAY 30</span>
